<TITLE>Crisis deepens in Tripura</TITLE>
<TEXT>
Tripura Central University authority had to step back from the decision to send Dean Arts Commerce in waiting anticipating further trouble for Vice Chancellor Prof A K Ghosh who is accused of series of corruption during his four years tenure A section of university teachers raised allegation against Dean Arts Commerce Prof Satyadeo Poddar for approving illegal academic activities of VC in past few months and also involved in screening process of candidature of the aspirants to the post of associate professor in four departments While demanding removal of VC immediately the teachers also asked for suspension of Dean Prof Poddar and instituting independent inquiry into the entire volume of purchase and appointments done during the tenure of incumbent VC Prof Ghosh Following pressure from the teachers and to save his skin VC committed to the agitating teachers that he would remove Prof Poddar from Deanship But Prof Poddar fought back to VC accusing him of compelling each and every one of the university administration to regularise his decisions Not only in case of recruitment The VC is the final authority of taking all the decisions including academic activities In several instances VC made us comply to perform in according to his choice and some cases we forced him to change the decision In particular case of elevation of an assistant professor to associate in Rural Development Department I was on leave and this was scrutinised by other Deans How can I be responsible for this VC must clarify before taking any action against me Prof Poddar told openly in the meeting of the administrative committee The university administration had stepped back from the decision after Prof Poddar raised voice Meantime a group of teachers stand behind Prof Poddar and ultimately revolt against VC and Register They however also demanded inquiry into the allegations by an independent authority to unearth the truth and added Academic atmosphere has gone down drastically in the university because of maladministration and students and scholars did not get any support for attending seminar and workshop while VC and his team has been looting out the public fund Earlier VC had recruited librarian deputy librarian finance officer and many other important posts of the university adopting unfair means and accused of a large scale corruption of procuring e book in the university The VC favoured a teacher in screening for elevation of associate professor who has engaged his daughter in Rural Development department under a project The VC is also accused of dedicating a furnish building and provided funding to one NGO run by his wife they alleged UNI BB KK
